**[[奇库尔金瑙尔语|奇库尔金瑙尔语]]
**[[金瑙尔语|金瑙尔语]]
**Thebor: [[Sunam_language|Sunam]]、[[Jangshung_language|Jangshung]]、[[Shumcho_language|Shumcho]]
*拉豪尔语组：[[Pattani_language|Pattani]] (Manchad)、[[蒂南语|蒂南语]]
*[[布南语|布南语]]
*[[Kanashi_language|Kanashi]]
*Rongpo–阿尔莫拉语组
**[[Rongpo_language|Rongpo]]
**阿尔莫拉语组：[[Darmiya_language|Darmiya]]、[[Byangsi_language|Byangsi]]、[[Dhuleli_language|Dhuleli]]、[[Chaudangsi_language|Chaudangsi]]、[[Rangas_language|Rangas]] (20世纪早期灭绝)、[[<font_color="#6666ff">象雄语</font>|<font color="#6666ff">象雄语</font>]]

[[象雄语|象雄语]]是[[苯教|苯教]]的神圣语言，分布在喜马拉雅山脉北麓，在藏语扩张至此之前横贯[[西藏|西藏]]西部。[[詹姆斯·马提索夫|詹姆斯·马提索夫]] (2001)<ref>Matisoff, James. 2001. "The interest of Zhangzhung for comparative Tibeto-Burman." In ''New Research on Zhangzhung and Related Himalayan Languages'' (Bon Studies 3). Senri Ethnological Studies no. 19. 大阪: 国立民族学博物館. {{doi|10.15021/00002145}}</ref>{{rp|155-180}}给出了象雄语属于西喜马拉雅语支的词汇和音系证据。

==系属分类==
Widmer (2014:47)<ref name="Widmer2014">Widmer, Manuel. 2014. "A tentative classification of West Himalayish." In ''A descriptive grammar of Bunan''. Ph.D. dissertation, University of Bern.</ref>{{rp|33-56}}的西喜马拉雅语支分类如下。最近新发现的[[Dhuleli_language|Dhuleli]]在Regmi & Prasain (2017)中加入。<ref name="Regmi">Regmi, Dan Raj; Prasain, Balaram. 2017. ''A sociolinguistic survey of Dhuleli''. Linguistic Survey of Nepal (LinSuN), Tribhuvan University, Kathmandu, Nepal.</ref>
;西喜马拉雅语支
*西部语群
**拉豪尔语组：[[Pattani_language|Manchad]]、[[蒂南语|蒂南语]]
**金瑙尔语组：[[Kanashi_language|Kanashi]]、下金瑙尔语、标准[[金瑙尔语|金瑙尔语]]、奇库尔金瑙尔语、Jangrami、[[Shumcho_language|Shumcho]]
*东部语群
**中部语组：[[布南语|布南语]]、[[Sunam_language|Sunnami]]、[[Rongpo_language|Rongpo]]; possibly [[象雄语|象雄语]]
**阿尔莫拉语组：[[Rangas_language|Rangas]]、[[Darmiya_language|Darmiya]]、[[Byangsi_language|Byangsi]]、[[Dhuleli_language|Dhuleli]]、[[Chaudangsi_language|Chaudangsi]]

Widmer (2014:53-56)<ref name="Widmer2014"/>还将[[象雄语|象雄语]]划入西喜马拉雅语支东部语群，并注意到它出现得和中部语组的语言([[布南语|布南语]]、[[Sunam_language|Sunnami]]和[[Rongpo_language|Rongpo]])特别近。

Widmer (2017)<ref name="Widmer2017">Widmer, Manuel. 2017. ''[https://www.academia.edu/34126236/The_linguistic_prehistory_of_the_western_Himalayas_endangered_minority_languages_as_a_window_to_the_past The linguistic prehistory of the western Himalayas: endangered minority languages as a window to the past] {{Wayback|url=https://www.academia.edu/34126236/The_linguistic_prehistory_of_the_western_Himalayas_endangered_minority_languages_as_a_window_to_the_past |date=20210730092910 }}''. Presented at Panel on Endangered Languages and Historical Linguistics, 23rd International Conference on Historical Linguistics (ICHL 23), San Antonio, Texas.</ref>注意到[[青藏高原|青藏高原]]西部许多[[藏语方言|藏语方言]]都曾被西喜马拉雅语支语言影响过。

